[ProMED-mail thanks Prof Berger for this interesting background
information. It helps put the 17 Jun 2010 report (ProMED-mail archive no.
20100617.2035) in perspective and answers the question about routine
vaccination against JE virus. The decline in JE cases over time is good
news, indeed.

A map of Viet Nam can be accessed at
<http://www.lib.utexas.edu/maps/middle_east_and_asia/vietnam_pol01.jpg>. A
